QueryText: Asking about the management of blast in rice.
KCCAns: I advised him to follow chemical method by suggesting him to spray some chemicals such as Carbendazim 50WP @ 500g/ha, Azoxystrobin 25 SC @ 500 ml/ha etc.

QueryText: QUERY REGARDING TRAINING ON BEE KEEPING
KCCAns: ADVICED TO CONTACT KRISHI VIGYAN KENDRA. CONTACT NO PROVIDED
ADVISED HIM TO APPLY CLASSIC 20 @ 2 ML / LITRE OF WATER.

QueryText: ASKING ABOUT THE USE OF UREA AS A TOP DRESS IN SALI RICE.
KCCAns: ADVISED HIM TO APPLY UREA AS A TOP DRESS IN SALI RICE @ 4.5 KG / BIGHA.

QueryText: ASKING FOR THE VITAMIN OF BRINJAL
KCCAns: RECOMMENDED TO SPRAY TRACEL @2ML PER LITRE

QueryText: Management of Green leaf hopper in rice
KCCAns: I suggested in him to spray either Phosalone 35 EC or Chloriphyriphos 20 EC @ 2ml/litre
